{"prompt": "Generate a website for a freelance design agency. The website should be artistic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Crimson Canvas Design</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #A00000;\n            --secondary-color: #D04040;\n            --accent-color: #F0E0E0;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --bg-color: #FFFFFF;\n            --dark-text-color: #FFFFFF;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--bg-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.8em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            height: 60vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        #hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: -50px;\n            left: -50px;\n            width: 200px;\n            height: 200px;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        #services h2, #portfolio h2, #contact h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-item, .portfolio-item {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover, .portfolio-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3, .portfolio-item h3 {\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item p, .portfolio-item p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n\n        #portfolio .portfolio-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .portfolio-item img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        #contact {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n        }\n\n        #contact h2 {\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n        }\n\n        #contact form {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        #contact label {\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n\n        #contact input[type=\"text\"],\n        #contact input[type=\"email\"],\n        #contact textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n        }\n\n        #contact textarea {\n            resize: vertical;\n            min-height: 150px;\n        }\n\n        #contact button {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        #contact button:hover {\n            background-color: #E03030;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 10px;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .nav-links {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .nav-links li {\n            display: inline;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n        }\n\n        .nav-links a {\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .nav-links a:hover {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        /* Artistic Flourish */\n        .brush-stroke {\n            position: relative;\n            display: inline-block;\n        }\n\n        .brush-stroke::after {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            bottom: -5px;\n            left: 50%;\n            transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(-3deg);\n            width: 110%;\n            height: 10px;\n            background: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(160,0,0,0.5), rgba(160,0,0,0.5) 5px, transparent 5px, transparent 10px);\n            z-index: -1;\n        }\n         .brush-stroke-secondary::after {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            bottom: -5px;\n            left: 50%;\n            transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(3deg);\n            width: 110%;\n            height: 8px;\n            background: repeating-linear-gradient(-45deg, rgba(208,64,64,0.4), rgba(208,64,64,0.4) 4px, transparent 4px, transparent 8px);\n            z-index: -1;\n        }\n\n        #hero .brush-stroke-secondary::after {\n            transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(0deg);\n            width: 120%;\n            height: 15px;\n             background: repeating-linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.3), rgba(255,255,255,0.3) 5px, transparent 5px, transparent 10px);\n        }\n\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1 class=\"brush-stroke\">Crimson Canvas Design</h1>\n            <p>Artful Branding & Visual Storytelling</p>\n            <nav>\n                <ul class=\"nav-links\">\n                    <li><a href=\"#services\">Services</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#portfolio\">Portfolio</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n                </ul>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2 class=\"brush-stroke-secondary\">Where Ideas Ignite and Visions Take Form</h2>\n            <p>We transform concepts into captivating visual experiences.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2 class=\"brush-stroke\">Our Creative Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Brand Identity Design</h3>\n                <p>Crafting unique logos, color palettes, and brand guidelines that speak your story.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Web & UI/UX Design</h3>\n                <p>Designing intuitive and aesthetically pleasing digital interfaces.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Artistic Illustrations</h3>\n                <p>Creating bespoke illustrations for marketing, editorial, and personal projects.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"portfolio\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2 class=\"brush-stroke\">Featured Work</h2>\n            <div class=\"portfolio-grid\">\n                <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x250/A00000/FFFFFF?text=Project+Alpha\" alt=\"Project Alpha Thumbnail\">\n                    <h3>Project Alpha</h3>\n                    <p>Innovative branding for a tech startup.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x250/D04040/FFFFFF?text=Project+Beta\" alt=\"Project Beta Thumbnail\">\n                    <h3>Project Beta</h3>\n                    <p>Engaging web design for a creative agency.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x250/F0E0E0/333333?text=Project+Gamma\" alt=\"Project Gamma Thumbnail\">\n                    <h3>Project Gamma</h3>\n                    <p>Whimsical illustrations for a children's book.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2 class=\"brush-stroke-secondary\">Let's Create Together</h2>\n            <p>Have a project in mind? We'd love to hear from you!</p>\n            <form id=\"contact-form\">\n                <label for=\"name\">Name:</label>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"email\">Email:</label>\n                <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"message\">Message:</label>\n                <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" required></textarea>\n\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Crimson Canvas Design. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p>\n                <a href=\"#\">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href=\"#\">Terms of Service</a>\n            </p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.getElementById('contact-form').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault();\n            alert('Message sent! We will be in touch soon.');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}